Puppet module: phpkb

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages phpkb software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include phpkb              # Install and run phpkb with standard configurations.
include phpkb::disable     # Disable phpkb service.
include phpkb::disableboot # Disable phpkb service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include phpkb::absent      # Remove phpkb package.

DEPENDENCIES:
